&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our leading SaaS-based Global Employment Platform™ enables clients to expand into over 180 countries quickly and efficiently, without the complexities of establishing local entities. At G-P, we’re dedicated to breaking down barriers to global business and creating opportunities for everyone, everywhere.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our diverse, remote-first teams are essential to our success. We empower our Dream Team members with flexibility and resources, fostering an environment where innovation thrives and every contribution is valued and celebrated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The work you do here will positively impact lives around the world. We stand by our promise: Opportunity Made Possible. In addition to competitive compensation and benefits, we invite you to join us in expanding your skills and helping to reshape the future of work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At G-P, we assist organizations in building exceptional global teams in days, not months—streamlining the hiring, onboarding, and management process to unlock growth potential for all.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the position:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;We are dedicated to pushing the boundaries of artificial intelligence and natural language processing. Our innovative team is committed to developing cutting-edge solutions that will revolutionize the AI landscape. We are passionate about our work and strive to create a positive impact on people&#39;s lives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;We are currently seeking a talented and highly motivated Computer Science 3rd year Intern to join our Generative AI and NLP team. This is a unique opportunity for a driven individual to contribute to the development of cutting-edge AI technology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Collaborate with our team of AI experts to develop and optimize generative AI and NLP models&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Conduct research on state-of-the-art techniques and algorithms in the AI and NLP domain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Contribute to the design, implementation, and evaluation of novel AI and NLP solutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Analyse and interpret data to improve model performance and efficiency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Assist in the documentation and presentation of research findings and project results&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Participate in team meetings and contribute to the ongoing development of the team&#39;s goals and objectives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Execute automated and manual tests for AI systems, focusing on minimizing issues like hallucination.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Work with AI engineers and data scientists to troubleshoot and optimize AI/ML models and pipelines.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we are looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Minimum Requirements:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Currently pursuing or recently completed a Bachelor&#39;s or Master&#39;s degree in Computer Science or a related field&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Strong proficiency in Python programming language, with experience in relevant AI and NLP libraries (e.g., TensorFlow, PyTorch, NLTK, spaCy)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Demonstrable passion for artificial intelligence, with a focus on generative AI and NLP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Familiarity with machine learning algorithms and concepts, such as supervised/unsupervised learning, deep learning, and neural networks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with the ability to learn quickly and adapt to new technologies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills, with the ability to collaborate effectively in a team setting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Experience with cloud computing platforms (e.g., AWS, Google Cloud Platform, Azure)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Knowledge of version control systems (e.g., Git) and software development methodologies (e.g., Agile)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Previous experience with AI or NLP research or projects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;A 12-week, full-time, paid internship for a 3rd year student with the opportunity to work on real-world AI and NLP projects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;A collaborative, supportive, and inclusive work environment where you can grow and learn from experienced professional&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;Access to state-of-the-art tools and resources to further your learning and development&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;The opportunity to contribute and make a meaningful impact in the AI industry&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;The annual gross base salary range for this position is $75,000 (prorated over 12 weeks)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
